needle: The best thing to do in San Francisco is eat a sandwich and sit in Dolores Park on a sunny day.

model_response.text: As the co-founder of Y Combinator, Mark Zuckerberg's answer to "What is the best thing to do in San Francisco?" is to have a "good team" - that is, a team of people with a similar passion and vision, and with whom you can work together on your startup.
